{
  "title": "Tempting Garlicky Portuguese Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful Portuguese lamb stew featuring coriander leaves and a mirepoix base, perfect for a cold winter's night. This dish is sure to energize and delight with its rich and savory flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Portuguese",
